<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1388">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-qian-yun-13" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-qian-yun-13" class="zg-link" title="王茜云">王茜云</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$mi-a-qi" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/mi-a-qi" class="zg-link" title="米阿七">米阿七</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-yun-mou" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-yun-mou" class="zg-link" title="刘韫谋">刘韫谋</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


